data.description: CORNER HOUSE!!! Beautiful and remodeled, with three bedrooms, two bathrooms, two-car garage, storage, lanai with screen; very close to I-75, Banks, Restaurants, downtown Fort Myers, shopping centers and beach. All renovations were done in 2023 (with permit) and include electricity, plumbing, sheetrock, insulation, floors and paint. The roof was installed in 2021.
